#jobs made with the help of crontab to automate any script

run below to check any present crontab job
crontab -l

run below to make a crontab
crontab -e
once it open in vi
place below line 
#* * * * * echo "hello world" >> /home/am92370/deepak/script/mycronjob.txt
#* * * * * /bin/ksh /home/am92370/deepak/script/myjob.ksh

remove # and update accordingly

now as per crontab create any script like in mycase it was myjob.ksh
